{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_017vmC1zNQWTDxKCTGDkkW48","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have all the information I need. Let me write all the required files.\n\n[1/10] 上游研判 — moltnet 是纯 Go 1.24 服务端 + Astro/TypeScript 嵌入式 web console，无官方 Docker 镜像，默认监听 8787 端口，SQLite 存储（`modernc.org/sqlite` 纯 Go 实现，无 CGO），auth 默认 `none`（无登录），健康检查端点 `/healthz`。\n\n[2/10] 移植路线 — `upstream_with_target_template`：多阶段 Dockerfile（Node→Go→Alpine runtime），`github_release` 检测版本，单服务 `moltnet`，无外部数据库依赖。"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1105,"cache_read_input_tokens":56143,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1105},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e426fc47-d3e7-4f68-b726-914dcf40f371","uuid":"d492df36-ec1f-4b0b-880a-cae08cdbe6d1"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_017vmC1zNQWTDxKCTGDkkW48","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01UjZRHhf76moXB99hxzhwSB","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"python3 - << 'EOF'\nimport struct, zlib\n\ndef create_png(width, height, r, g, b):\n    def chunk(kind, data):\n        c = kind + data\n        return struct.pack('>I', len(data)) + c + struct.pack('>I', zlib.crc32(c) & 0xffffffff)\n    \n    sig = b'\\x89PNG\\r\\n\\x1a\\n'\n    ihdr = chunk(b'IHDR', struct.pack('>IIBBBBB', width, height, 8, 2, 0, 0, 0))\n    raw = b''\n    row = bytes([0] + [r, g, b] * width)\n    for _ in range(height):\n        raw += row\n    idat = chunk(b'IDAT', zlib.compress(raw, 9))\n    iend = chunk(b'IEND', b'')\n    png = sig + ihdr + idat + iend\n    with open('/__w/lzcat-apps/lzcat-apps/apps/moltnet/icon.png', 'wb') as f:\n        f.write(png)\n    print(f'Written {len(png)} bytes')\n\n# Moltnet brand green #3ddc84 = RGB(61,220,132)\ncreate_png(512, 512, 61, 220, 132)\nEOF","description":"Create 512x512 moltnet brand-green icon.png"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1105,"cache_read_input_tokens":56143,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1105},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e426fc47-d3e7-4f68-b726-914dcf40f371","uuid":"a06c36a5-5cd5-45ea-8bf9-bdf6eb90d410"}
